title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update 16 - Caribbean
description:
In this video we will look at the new additions to World Update 16: Caribbean which will be released next week. The screenshots used in this video are based on the developer webcast which took place late last year where Asobo and Microsoft announced this world update. We have to wait until next week to try it out ourself.
